{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"725c5b083d","title":"周恩来传达毛泽东有关江西省军区报告的批示及他自己的指示","origin":"1967年10月江西省直机关保卫毛泽东思想联合战斗团、江西省无产阶级革命派大联合筹委会新闻界联络站编印的《毛主席无限关怀江西  中央首长对江西问题的指示》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19da8d50bf","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":30,"articleId":"725c5b083d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9073865ccd","name":"江西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2b9e0ccf6","type":"title","text":"周恩来传达毛泽东有关江西省军区报告的批示及他自己的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"ee49d1b542","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"1039d82e1d","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：1967年5月30凌晨2：10〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"3196836a6a","type":"appellation","text":"五月三十日凌晨二时十分周总理来电话，转告了毛主席在一个文件上的批语：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"07c4d3070a","type":"appellation","text":"林彪、恩来同志、文革小组同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"5160c893ef","type":"paragraph","text":"江西军区与革命群众的对立情绪为什么愈演愈烈？江西军区某些负责同志对待群众的态度是否正确，值得研究。此外，还有××、××、××三个省军区对待群众的态度是否对，也值得研究。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"1220888e1c","type":"paragraph","text":" 刘培善（签字）6.1","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"05abfe7f76","type":"paragraph","text":"同时总理指示：","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"1f31c6514f","type":"paragraph","text":"1．江西军区在“三支”、“两军”中犯了一些缺点错误，革命群众认为犯了方向路线性错误。你们应该很好解决。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"821540d803","type":"paragraph","text":"2．江西日报问题不要争论下去了，“江西日报”四个字可以暂时去掉，改出一个时期的新华电讯。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"630c36fb13","type":"paragraph","text":"3．不要把刘瑞森的问题看得太严重了。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"},{"id":"78f78e89e1","type":"paragraph","text":"4．刘培善先作检查，军区那个检查，你们（指军区）自己研究。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d"}],"page":{"id":"a37f30d9e4","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"725c5b083d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}